title: FK Vardarski
text:
FK Vardarski () was a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club from <a href="Bogdanci">Bogdanci</a>, <a href="Republic%20of%20Macedonia">Republic of Macedonia</a>. They were recently played in the <a href="Macedonian%20Regional%20Leagues">OFS Gevgelija</a> league.
History.
The club was founded in 1969. Their greatest success are the playing in the <a href="Macedonian%20First%20Football%20League">Macedonian First Football League</a> in the inaugural season (<a href="1992%E2%80%9393%20Macedonian%20First%20Football%20League">1992–93</a>).
<a href="Cvetan%20%C4%8Curlinov">Cvetan Churlinov</a> started his career with the team.
